          <b><span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">Νεοπτόλεμος</span></b> :
            <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">Neoptolemus</span>, the son of Achilles, reared in Scyros,
          conducts the Myrmidons home from Troy, and weds Hermione, the daughter
          of Menelāus, <i><span class="en">Il. 19.327</span></i>, <i><span class="en">Od. 3.189</span></i>, <i><span class="en">Od.
            4.5</span></i>, <i><span class="en">Od. 11.520</span></i>.</div> <div class="alpheios-lex-footnotes en"> </div>
